_sText:
This map is just alittle test, to see how easy it is to make a map. It isnt 100% fixed for bugs so if you find any please post it or contact me on my mail "Nikvestergaard@yahoo.dk". If you got any ideas to upgrades on the map or a new map i should try to make please also contact me.

This map is a simpel "aim_deagle" map where the CT's spawns in the south of the hall and the T's starts in the north, then like alot other aim maps is there alot of box-/crates. The map does also contain 1 secret "tunnel" wich you guys can have fun by finding :)

Thanks to all who downloads it.
